flowchart TB

    DEV[Developer]

    GIT[GitHub Repository]

    PR[Pull Request]

    CI[GitHub Actions CI]

    TEST[Automated Tests]

    BUILD[Build Validation]

    PREVIEW[Vercel Preview]

    STAGING[Staging Environment]

    PROD[Production Environment]

    SUPA[Supabase Project]

    MIG[Database Migrations]

    EDGE[Edge Functions]

    MON[Monitoring]

    DEV --> GIT
    GIT --> PR
    PR --> CI
    CI --> TEST
    TEST --> BUILD
    BUILD --> PREVIEW
    PREVIEW --> STAGING
    STAGING --> PROD

    CI --> MIG
    MIG --> SUPA
    CI --> EDGE
    EDGE --> SUPA

    PROD --> MON
    SUPA --> MON